{% endblock %}

{% block speech_style %}Speaks with a refined Altmer accent, using precise vocabulary and formal sentence structure. Delivers words deliberately with slight condescension. Tends toward economy of expression when discussing business but becomes eloquent when describing craftsmanship. Voice carries a melodic quality typical of Altmer, though hardened by Winterhold's harsh conditions. Punctuates statements with subtle hand gestures when emphasizing quality or value.{% endblock %}